  "detailed_description": "The Guardian Stone is a third person Action Tower Defense Game with Rpg elements and multiplayer. Set in the fantasy world of Elrone, You play as a hero protecting the realm from the forces of evil.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/d96f1cdf8f05a77adf596b2149f470fd.poster.avif?t=1669008185\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/d96f1cdf8f05a77adf596b2149f470fd.webm?t=1669008185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/d96f1cdf8f05a77adf596b2149f470fd.mp4?t=1669008185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/6404ea1287c0fa719791ea131ffcfa1d.poster.avif?t=1669008185\" width=640 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/6404ea1287c0fa719791ea131ffcfa1d.webm?t=1669008185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/6404ea1287c0fa719791ea131ffcfa1d.mp4?t=1669008185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play the entire game Solo or with up to 3 friends online.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/8cdd36c7c164f26a2bddcd783753b3f7.poster.avif?t=1669008185\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/8cdd36c7c164f26a2bddcd783753b3f7.webm?t=1669008185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/8cdd36c7c164f26a2bddcd783753b3f7.mp4?t=1669008185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Test your Strategy and skills inside the arena, and check out the player vs player mode where one player takes control of the map and spawns waves of enemy's, with the ability to posses and take direct control of any character they spawn.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/801254039614fa7cbb7b9f408dc0a807.poster.avif?t=1669008185\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/801254039614fa7cbb7b9f408dc0a807.webm?t=1669008185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/801254039614fa7cbb7b9f408dc0a807.mp4?t=1669008185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Featuring a leveling system with unlockable skills, a talent tree and weapon abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/0a5f99023c0a29f9a26bc68ddc6278b7.poster.avif?t=1669008185\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/0a5f99023c0a29f9a26bc68ddc6278b7.webm?t=1669008185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/0a5f99023c0a29f9a26bc68ddc6278b7.mp4?t=1669008185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Find Pets and companions with special abilities to help you get through the more challenging levels.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/3366b72f22f6111bf6aa526df5ab3a4e.poster.avif?t=1669008185\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/3366b72f22f6111bf6aa526df5ab3a4e.webm?t=1669008185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/3366b72f22f6111bf6aa526df5ab3a4e.mp4?t=1669008185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663860/extras/cc2f993bac52d0cecf119abeb057bf8f.avif?t=1669008185\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>Join the Guardian Stone Discord to keep up with the development!<br>",
